query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag AS t
inner join site AS s
on t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('dockerfile',
'grouping',
'hiveql',
'material-design') AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND tq.site_id = s.site_id
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000;
